## Limitations

The information gathered is limited to the sources available up to October 2023, and some sources may not have the most current data due to the rapidly evolving nature of climate policy. Additionally, the effectiveness of these strategies can vary significantly based on regional and political contexts, which are not fully explored in this report. Further research could include more recent data and a broader range of international perspectives.